flowchart TD
    A["Code change or promotion request"] --> B["Jenkins pipeline start"]
    B --> C["Prepare workspace<br/>resolve commit id and create security-reports directory"]
    C --> D{"Target environment"}

    D -->|dev| E["Run Gitleaks"]
    E --> F["Run OWASP Dependency-Check"]
    F --> G["Run kube-score on Kubernetes manifests"]
    G --> H["Build Docker image"]
    H --> I["Push image to Azure Container Registry"]
    I --> J["Run Trivy image scan"]
    J --> K["Render manifests with envsubst"]

    D -->|qa / uat / prod| L["Promote image<br/>pull tag from previous environment and push new tag"]
    L --> K

    K --> M["SSH to jump server and copy manifests with SCP"]
    M --> N["Create namespace if missing"]
    N --> O["kubectl apply manifests"]
    O --> P["Wait for deployment rollout status"]
    P --> Q{"dev environment?"}
    Q -->|yes| R["Upload security reports to Azure Storage Account"]
    Q -->|no| S["Pipeline complete"]
    R --> S
